  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_62",
    "english": "Taimanin. The owner of Gosha's snack shop \"Inageya\", who excels in making ice cream or wagashi. She has a creed of opening Inageya every day, and does not tolerate anyone who disturbs her.\n \nBack in the day, she was one of the top Taimanins, and rumor has it that she still goes out on missions at night. She can neutralize any human or demon by stabbing them in their acupuncture points, and uses Soul Art to manipulate life energy and exchanges them however she wants to cope with various situations.",
    "japanese": "Taimanin. The owner of Gosha's snack shop \"Inageya\", who excels in making ice cream or wagashi. She has a creed of opening Inageya every day, and does not tolerate anyone who disturbs her.\n \nBack in the day, she was one of the top Taimanins, and rumor has it that she still goes out on missions at night. She can neutralize any human or demon by stabbing them in their acupuncture points, and uses Soul Art to manipulate life energy and exchanges them however she wants to cope with various situations.",
    "korean": "Taimanin. The owner of Gosha's snack shop \"Inageya\", who excels in making ice cream or wagashi. She has a creed of opening Inageya every day, and does not tolerate anyone who disturbs her.\n \nBack in the day, she was one of the top Taimanins, and rumor has it that she still goes out on missions at night. She can neutralize any human or demon by stabbing them in their acupuncture points, and uses Soul Art to manipulate life energy and exchanges them however she wants to cope with various situations.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin. The owner of Gosha's snack shop \"Inageya\", who excels in making ice cream or wagashi. She has a creed of opening Inageya every day, and does not tolerate anyone who disturbs her.\n \nBack in the day, she was one of the top Taimanins, and rumor has it that she still goes out on missions at night. She can neutralize any human or demon by stabbing them in their acupuncture points, and uses Soul Art to manipulate life energy and exchanges them however she wants to cope with various situations.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. The owner of Gosha's snack shop \"Inageya\", who excels in making ice cream or wagashi. She has a creed of opening Inageya every day, and does not tolerate anyone who disturbs her.\n \nBack in the day, she was one of the top Taimanins, and rumor has it that she still goes out on missions at night. She can neutralize any human or demon by stabbing them in their acupuncture points, and uses Soul Art to manipulate life energy and exchanges them however she wants to cope with various situations.",
    "spanish": "Taimanin. The owner of Gosha's snack shop \"Inageya\", who excels in making ice cream or wagashi. She has a creed of opening Inageya every day, and does not tolerate anyone who disturbs her.\n \nBack in the day, she was one of the top Taimanins, and rumor has it that she still goes out on missions at night. She can neutralize any human or demon by stabbing them in their acupuncture points, and uses Soul Art to manipulate life energy and exchanges them however she wants to cope with various situations."
